    <div class="base">
        <div class="section gray_section">
            <div class="section_inner">
                <div class="section_content text_block"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Looking%20to%20get%20started%20with%20Lisk?%20Simply%20follow%20our%205%20step%20guide%20and%20get%20involved!&amp;url=https://lisk.io/get_started" class="material-icons consensus_btn">share</a>
                    <div class="get_started_block">
                        <p>Welcome to Lisk! We are glad you found your way to us and hope that Lisk is the right platform for you! <!--Below you find a short introduction video about Lisk.--> Further down you find 6 steps which we think are vital for a great Lisk experience. Please follow them carefully if this is your first time with Lisk.</p>
                        <!--<p class="text_center"><iframe width="100%" height="438px" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O9o5X4xHJnc?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>-->
                        <p class="text_center text_center_mob btns_v1"><a href="https://lisk.chat/" class="btn_v2 normal_btn blue_btn" target="_blank">Join our Chat</a> <a href="https://forum.lisk.io/" class="btn_v2 normal_btn white_btn" target="_blank">Our Forum</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
